    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/fr-hellodarknessmyoldfriend/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=609023964185887704&sectionId=609024031898731480)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU5PwO8ES1_text","label":"ggU5PwO8ES1_text","default":"Matcha Energy Meets&nbsp;<br>Beauty Collagen"},{"type":"html","id":"ggczQlFQuMx_text","label":"ggczQlFQuMx_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">☀️ <strong>More energy, focus with no jitters</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">🥥 <strong>Delicious coconut and vanilla flavours</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">🥛 <strong>Super easy to mix with milk, water etc</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">✨ <strong>Glowing skin, hair &amp; nails support</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTMwAK8DSU_label","label":"ggTMwAK8DSU_label","default":"ADD TO CART"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTMwAK8DSU_outOfStockLabel","label":"ggTMwAK8DSU_outOfStockLabel","default":"Out of stock"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTMwAK8DSU_unavailableLabel","label":"ggTMwAK8DSU_unavailableLabel","default":"Unavailable"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTMwAK8DSU_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","label":"ggTMwAK8DSU_variantSelectionRequiredMessage","default":"Please select a variant to add product to cart"},{"type":"html","id":"ggybyXK4vI5_text","label":"ggybyXK4vI5_text","default":"<p>Free Shipping on Orders $50+</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxrBsoh4hk_text","label":"ggxrBsoh4hk_text","default":"<p>\"I’ve convinced all of my friends to switch from <strong>coffee to Teangle matcha collagen</strong>.”</p><p>Emily K. ✓ Verified Customer</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_0","label":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_0","default":"<p>Why You'll Love It</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_1","label":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_1","default":"<p>Taste &amp; Feel</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_2","label":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_2","default":"<p>How to Enjoy</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_3","label":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_3","default":"<p>Is This For You?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_4","label":"ggnW-zlbTEF_childItem_4","default":"<p>Ingredients &amp; Quality</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfZlhvHMuV_text","label":"ggfZlhvHMuV_text","default":"<p>Matcha Collagen+ is your new delicious ritual where matcha energy meets collagen beauty without the afternoon crash</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>- Supports skin, hair, joints and nail health&nbsp;</p><p>- Helps increase energy, focus and clarity<br>- Two flavours: Original (Coconuty) and Vanilla<br>- Easy to mix, hot or cold, in drinks or food<br>- No added sugar, dairy, gluten, or weird stuff</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYwsvXRD_l_text","label":"ggYwsvXRD_l_text","default":"<p>Matcha Collagen+ comes in two delicious flavours:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Original: Smooth with a light coconutty finish<br>Vanilla: Subtle, creamy, and naturally sweet</p><p><br>And the feel? Calm and sustained energy, no jitters, no crash. Just focus, glow, and a little daily “ahhh.”</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9FxdHduyz_text","label":"gg9FxdHduyz_text","default":"<p>Enjoy it your way - hot or iced, in the morning or as an afternoon boost.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Just add a scoop to water, milk, or your favourite alt-milk. It dissolves easily and tastes great every time.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Want to get creative?</p><p>You’ll get our free 101 Matcha Recipes book with your first order - packed with easy ideas like smoothies, snacks, baked treats, and more.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>There’s no wrong way to matcha.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQvk1UkYw3_text","label":"ggQvk1UkYw3_text","default":"<p>If you're looking for a healthy daily ritual that actually makes you feel good - this is for you.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You want to replace coffee but still feel energized<br>You want healthier skin, hair, nails and a glow<br>You want collagen, but not in pill, capsule, or powder<br>You care about clean ingredients and no added sugars<br>You want something quick, easy, and actually delicious<br>Sounds like you? You’ll love Matcha Collagen.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUNyRmu8Q4_text","label":"ggUNyRmu8Q4_text","default":"<p>When it comes to ingredients, taste, and trust, Teangle stands out. We kept the good stuff (like organic matcha and marine collagen) and ditched the junk.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OG Flavor: 5g of pure marine collagen, 1g of organic ceremonial Matcha, organic coconut milk powder and organic acacia gum</p><p>ALLERGEN: FISH</p>"}],
